
Zarafa-Postfixadmin is created with postfixadmin 2.93


Install

Insert in server-block of nginx config ... include /etc/webapps/zarafa-postfixadmin/nginx-location.conf; 
Insert in /etc/php/php-fpm.conf ... include=/etc/php/fpm.d/*.conf

Run ... systemctl restart php-fpm
Run ... /usr/share/doc/zarafa-postfixadmin/install
Visit ... https://alarm/zarafa-postfixadmin/setup.php and create a superadmin account.

Run ... systemctl enable zarafa-postfixadmin-worker.service
Run ... systemctl enable zarafa-postfixadmin-worker.timer
Run ... systemctl start zarafa-postfixadmin-worker.service
